text: South Strafford is an unincorporated village in the town of Strafford, Orange County, Vermont, United States. The community is located along Vermont Route 132 northwest of Hanover, New Hampshire. South Strafford has a post office with ZIP code 05070. ==References== Category:Unincorporated communities in Orange County, Vermont Category:Unincorporated communities in Vermont
